{"tid":385410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部強烈譴責北韓再次核試","createTime":"2017-09-03T08:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T14:54:50.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba03d8fee6e6a50c1579a336c8f870fee7ac46a9","tid":385410,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"中國外交部發表聲明，強烈譴責北韓再次核試。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說，北韓不顧國際社會普遍反對，再次進行核子試驗，中國政府堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n外交部說，實現朝鮮半島無核化、維護核不擴散、維護東北亞和平穩定，是中方堅定立場，也是國際社會普遍意願。"},{"pid":"a59f5e737a9860b582d27fdbbaa99a37788d3db5","tid":385410,"uid":63400,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"It's boring"},{"pid":"a502d68136454621dc0f2b5b2f63349f9c8ed8dd","tid":385410,"uid":20809,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:13:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母中國口交部真係好撚易做，穫穫都講同一樣野。"},{"pid":"690c42f7f0a24fe63c3520fefc56bac4132a39cf","tid":385410,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"中國口交部發表聲"},{"pid":"a7ab9ea9cdbc4c82d663e8e2fc2fa367f5db0016","tid":385410,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"35be3004415e4b2e564c195986d01390ed852621","tid":385410,"uid":14503,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"其實中國口交部不如set個auto reply"},{"pid":"c59b695f4c429d8ee422bc6c6b3066e8748236e6","tid":385410,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d07594c4cbfc441d32b906233f5234692776b7b","tid":385410,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"同晴報記者一樣咁易做。<br />\n2016年9月9日以下聲明<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160909004693-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20160909004693-260409&d=bPK0oh70e0%2B6TKpohi9AyRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=67b51d3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160909004693-260409</a><br />\n聲明首段指出，「今天，朝鮮民主主義人民共和國不顧國際社會普遍反對，再次進行核試驗，中國政府對此表示堅決反對」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明第二段提到，實現朝鮮半島無核化、防止核擴散、維護東北亞和平穩定，是中方的堅定立場。「我們強烈敦促朝方信守無核化承諾，遵守安理會相關決議，停止採取任何惡化局勢的行動」。<br />\n<br />\n末段強調，「中方將同國際社會一道，堅定推進半島無核化目標，堅持通過六方會談解決有關問題」。"},{"pid":"81e06f6befdd520fc0672f88b7d41095244f6ae4","tid":385410,"uid":19004,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"template:<br />\n<br />\n中方敦促各方克制，<br />\n不要對半島作出無謂的挑釁，<br />\n以免引起局勢更進一步的惡化，<br />\n中方高度關注事件，<br />\n絕對不會坐視不理，希望各方以進行和平對話，<br />\n武力不能解決問題"},{"pid":"0b4f7a1b9e846421ac41a498b6f88cb7150cab7c","tid":385410,"uid":22326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>template:<br />\n<br />\n中方敦促各方克制，<br />\n不要對半島作出無謂的挑釁，<br />\n以免引起局勢更進一步的惡化，<br />\n中方高度關注事件，<br />\n絕對不會坐視不理，希望各方以進行和平對話，<br />\n武力不能解決問題</blockquote><br />\n真係咩情況都啱用，換個國家同地方名就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8652954b7afa389df3d92269547b04348e39a6be","tid":385410,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實中國口交部不如set個auto reply</blockquote><br />\n根本係BOT嚟"},{"pid":"a88d25702109dca4decc1f422a6b2da41ec0567b","tid":385410,"uid":140233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/94fb8e77jw1ea71kltxcfg20jk04cwer.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw1024%2F94fb8e77jw1ea71kltxcfg20jk04cwer.gif&h=8d0226a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb8e9ce2cea01afb3326369fc11a87037a8494f3","tid":385410,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/94fb8e77jw1e